<Layout title="About - Pantry Party">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About Pantry Party</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What is Pantry Party?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Pantry Party is a collaborative recipe generation app that brings people together 
          to create amazing meals. Whether you're planning a dinner with friends, cooking 
          with family, or just exploring new recipe ideas, Pantry Party makes it fun and easy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>
            <strong>Create or Join a Room:</strong> Start a new cooking session or join 
            an existing one with a room ID.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Add Ingredients:</strong> Everyone can contribute ingredients by typing, 
            speaking, or uploading photos.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Set Constraints:</strong> Specify dietary restrictions, allergies, meal 
            types, cooking methods, and time limits.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Generate Recipes:</strong> Our AI analyzes your ingredients and constraints 
            to create personalized recipe suggestions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Vote Together:</strong> Review the generated recipes and vote on your favorites 
            as a group.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cook and Enjoy:</strong> Select the winning recipe and get step-by-step 
            instructions to make it happen!
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

